settings.help_text:
Channel recommendations are precalculated periodically. One can choose the period based on [cron specifications](https://godoc.org/github.com/robfig/cron). Examples: 
 @daily - Run once a day, midnight. 
 @hourly - Run once an hour, beginning of hour. 
 @every 1h30m - Run every hour and thirty minutes. 
 The default is @daily
